data.description: Are you searching for a dream home that offers comfort, convenience, and a great location? Look no further! We are thrilled to present this stunning 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom, one-car garage. Colonial is nestled in a beautiful, manicured neighborhood and features a well-maintained lawn, providing excellent curb appeal. Don't miss out on the opportunity to call 81 Holbrook Lane your new home. With its stylish interior, appealing exterior, and fantastic location, this property has it all!!! Schedule a showing to experience firsthand the charm and comfort this home has to offer. Contingent upon the owner finding suitable housing within 60 days or less. Bonus pool!! Motivated seller. **Roof updated in 2021; AC updated in 2021; hot water updated in 2021.
